/********************************************************************/
/**
 * 1.  GETTING STARTED
 **/

    @Package:       MyNews-FGal
    @Creator:       Mike McMurray (alien@alienated.org)
    @Maintainer:    Mike McMurray (alien@alienated.org)

    Details:

    This Module is intended to extend the functionality of the
    MyNews-5 CMS (Content Management System) with a web based
    photo gallery.

    The files included with this MyNews-Module distribution are:

    $ MyNews-FGal/README
    $ MyNews-FGal/INSTALL
    $ MyNews-FGal/UPGRADING
    $ MyNews-FGal/htdocs/modules/conf/fgal.conf.php
    $ MyNews-FGal/htdocs/modules/fgal.php
    $ MyNews-FGal/htdocs/modules/lib/fgal.lib.php
    $ MyNews-FGal/htdocs/admin/fgaladmin.php
    $ MyNews-FGal/htdocs/admin/lib/fgaladmin.lib.php
    $ MyNews-FGal/sql/MyNews-FGal.sql
    $ MyNews-FGal/sql/MyNews-FGal-upgrade.sql

/********************************************************************/
/**
 * 2.  REQUIREMENTS
 **/

    - [1] MyNews CMS Framework - >= 5-RC1
    - [2] MyNews-FMan2 addon module.

[1] http://mynews.alienated.org/pub/MyNews/v5/MyNews-latest.tar.gz
[2] http://mynews.alienated.org/pub/MyNews/v5/Modules/
/********************************************************************/
/**
 * 3.  INSTALL
 **/

    - Please Refer to the included INSTALL file.

/********************************************************************/
/**
 * 4.  MISC
 **/

    This is port of the original "Photo Gallery" module for the
    Version 4 branch of the MyNews CMS which was also written and
    maintained by me (Mike McMurray).

